GSAS ASSOCIATED SCOPE OF WORK AND REQUEST FOR PROPOSAL DATED 08/17/2015 IS HEREBY INCORPORATED INTO THIS TASK ORDER. CFMS PROPOSAL ENTITLED 7TH FLOOR PROBATION OFFICE REPLACE CARPET, COVE BASE, AND PAINT, DATED FEBRUARY 22, 2016 AND PRICE OF $49,284.02 ARE HEREBY ACCEPTED BY GSA.
